---
// Landing page - custom layout, not Starlight
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Sidemesh - Your agent workstation, from anywhere</title>
<meta
  name="description"
  content="Sidemesh pairs a small daemon on your own Mac, VPS, or workstation with a mobile app for sessions, approvals, files, terminals, ports, and previews."
/>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#f6f1e8" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Sidemesh - Your agent workstation, from anywhere" />
<meta
  property="og:description"
  content="Run coding agents on your own machines and keep the host surface reachable from your phone or desktop."
/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:image" content="/assets/og-card-v1.png" />
<meta
  property="og:image:alt"
  content="Sidemesh illustration showing sessions, approvals, terminal access, browser preview, and port forwarding."
/>
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:image" content="/assets/og-card-v1.png" />
<meta
  name="twitter:image:alt"
  content="Sidemesh illustration showing sessions, approvals, terminal access, browser preview, and port forwarding."
/>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/favicon.png" />
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/app-icon.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link
  href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap"
  rel="stylesheet"
/>
<style>
  :root {
    --paper: #f6f1e8;
    --paper-strong: #efe6d7;
    --ink: #0f1827;
    --ink-soft: #4c596b;
    --line: rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.12);
    --line-soft: rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.08);
    --accent: #cf6e28;
    --accent-deep: #a55317;
    --route: #2f6a58;
    --shadow: 0 40px 120px -64px rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.4);
    --shadow-soft: 0 26px 72px -52px rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.28);
    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --wrap: min(1240px, calc(100% - 48px));
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }

  body {
    min-height: 100dvh;
    margin: 0;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    color: var(--ink);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, rgba(207, 110, 40, 0.12), transparent 30rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 10%, rgba(47, 106, 88, 0.08), transparent 30rem),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #fbf8f2 0%, var(--paper) 18%, #f5efe3 62%, #efe6d8 100%);
    font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.48;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  body::after {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
    content: "";
    opacity: 0.05;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 220 220' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.84' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='220' height='220' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.5'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  ::selection {
    background: rgba(207, 110, 40, 0.16);
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  p,
  li {
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  img {
    display: block;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .wrap {
    width: var(--wrap);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .mono {
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
  }

  .skip-link {
    position: fixed;
    top: 14px;
    left: 14px;
    z-index: 30;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.96);
    transform: translateY(-180%);
    transition: transform 180ms var(--ease);
  }

  .skip-link:focus {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    background: rgba(250, 246, 239, 0.84);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 78px;
  }

  .brand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .brand-logo {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(63, 35, 6, 0.14);
  }

  .nav-links,
  .footer-links {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .nav-links {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .nav-links a,
  .footer-links a {
    padding: 9px 11px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: background 180ms var(--ease), color 180ms var(--ease);
  }

  .nav-links a:hover,
  .nav-links a:focus-visible,
  .footer-links a:hover,
  .footer-links a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--ink);
    background: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.72);
  }

  .nav-cta {
    justify-self: end;
  }

  .button,
  .text-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 46px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition:
      transform 220ms var(--ease),
      color 220ms var(--ease),
      background 220ms var(--ease),
      border-color 220ms var(--ease),
      box-shadow 220ms var(--ease);
  }

  .button {
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #fff8ef;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .button:hover,
  .button:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    background: var(--accent-deep);
    border-color: var(--accent-deep);
  }

  .button.secondary {
    border-color: var(--line);
    background: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.72);
    color: var(--ink);
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .button.secondary:hover,
  .button.secondary:focus-visible {
    border-color: var(--ink);
    background: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.92);
  }

  .button:active,
  .text-link:active {
    transform: translateY(1px) scale(0.99);
  }

  .text-link {
    gap: 9px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .text-link::after {
    content: "->";
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .text-link:hover,
  .text-link:focus-visible {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    width: 34px;
    height: 1px;
    content: "";
    background: rgba(165, 83, 23, 0.34);
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding: 36px 0 54px;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .hero::before {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -2;
    content: "";
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.98) 0%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.92) 34%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.64) 55%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.12) 76%),
      url("/assets/og-card-v1.png");
    background-position: left top, 76% center;
    background-size: auto, cover;
  }

  .hero::after {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    content: "";
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 24%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.46), transparent 16rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at 94% 18%, rgba(47, 106, 88, 0.14), transparent 20rem);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    min-height: calc(100dvh - 114px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 36rem;
    padding: 42px 0 46px;
  }

  .hero-icon {
    position: absolute;
    right: -10.5rem;
    bottom: -1rem;
    width: clamp(160px, 26vw, 260px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    opacity: 0.95;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 34px 64px rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.18));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-copy h1 {
    margin: 24px 0 18px;
    max-width: 10ch;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.07em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-copy h1 span {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--route);
  }

  .hero-copy p {
    max-width: 33rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 28px 0 28px;
  }

  .command-strip {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
    width: max-content;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .command-strip span {
    display: block;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 11px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.72);
    overflow-x: auto;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .hero-facts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 34px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }

  .hero-facts div {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .hero-facts b {
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-facts p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .section {
    padding: 128px 0;
  }

  .lead {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 38px;
  }

  .lead h2 {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 11ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4.4vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .lead p {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .rails {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .rail {
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .rail strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .rail p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .mural {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 42px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .mural img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .mural-band {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    gap: 54px;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .mural-copy h3 {
    margin: 18px 0 14px;
    max-width: 10ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 3.8vw, 4.1rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .mural-copy p {
    max-width: 33rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .mural-tall {
    height: 620px;
  }

  .mural-tall img {
    object-position: 77% center;
  }

  .mural-wide {
    height: 420px;
    margin-top: 42px;
  }

  .mural-wide img {
    object-position: 84% 60%;
  }

  .install-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .install-step {
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .install-step b {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .install-step h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.04;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .install-step p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .install-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 22px;
  }

  .security {
    padding: 42px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }

  .security-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .security-grid h2 {
    margin: 18px 0 14px;
    max-width: 12ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .security-grid p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .route-lines {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .route-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .route-row strong {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .route-line {
    position: relative;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(15, 24, 39, 0.16);
  }

  .route-line::after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: 0;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    content: "";
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .faq {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .faq-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 280px) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 22px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }

  .faq-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }

  .faq-row strong {
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .faq-row p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .closing {
    position: relative;
    padding: 108px 0 92px;
  }

  .closing::before {
    position: absolute;
    right: 6%;
    bottom: 32px;
    width: clamp(120px, 14vw, 180px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 34px;
    content: "";
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
      url("/assets/app-icon.png") center / cover no-repeat;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    opacity: 0.92;
  }

  .closing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 28px;
    align-items: end;
    padding-top: 26px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .closing-grid h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    max-width: 12ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .closing-grid p {
    max-width: 35rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .closing-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 0 32px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.94rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1180px) {
    .hero::before {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.96) 0%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.88) 40%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.42) 100%),
        url("/assets/og-card-v1.png");
      background-position: left top, 62% center;
      background-size: auto, cover;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 41rem;
    }

    .hero-icon {
      right: 0;
      bottom: -2rem;
    }

    .mural-band,
    .security-grid,
    .closing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .closing-actions {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .nav-inner {
      grid-template-columns: auto auto;
      grid-template-areas:
        "brand cta"
        "links links";
      padding: 16px 0;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .brand {
      grid-area: brand;
    }

    .nav-links {
      grid-area: links;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      grid-area: cta;
    }

    .hero-facts,
    .rails,
    .install-grid,
    .faq-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 104px 0;
    }

    .hero-copy h1 {
      max-width: 8ch;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .hero::before {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.98) 0%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.94) 42%, rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.82) 100%),
        url("/assets/og-card-v1.png");
      background-position: left top, 70% top;
      background-size: auto, cover;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: min(100% - 28px, 1240px);
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding-top: 28px;
      padding-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .hero-copy h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 18vw, 5.1rem);
    }

    .hero-icon {
      position: relative;
      right: auto;
      bottom: auto;
      width: 132px;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .mural {
      border-radius: 28px;
    }

    .mural-tall,
    .mural-wide {
      height: 320px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 84px 0;
    }

    footer {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .button,
    .button.secondary {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .hero-actions,
    .install-actions,
    .closing-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .text-link {
      width: max-content;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <header class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Sidemesh home">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/assets/app-icon.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Sidemesh</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#what">What it is</a>
        <a href="#install">Install</a>
        <a href="#security">Security</a>
        <a href="/getting-started/">Docs</a>
      </nav>
      <a
        class="button secondary nav-cta"
        href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
      >
        Join iOS beta
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <span class="eyebrow">Private agent workstation</span>
          <h1>Your agent workstation, <span>from anywhere.</span></h1>
          <p>
            Sidemesh keeps agent work on the machines you already trust, then
            gives you the host surface around it: sessions, approvals, files,
            terminals, ports, previews, and the route between your devices.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button" href="#install">Install host</a>
            <a
              class="button secondary"
              href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join iOS beta
            </a>
            <a
              class="text-link"
              href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join Discord
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="command-strip mono" aria-label="Install commands">
            <span>$ npm install -g sidemesh @openai/codex</span>
            <span>$ sidemesh up</span>
          </div>
          <img
            class="hero-icon"
            src="/assets/app-icon.png"
            alt="Sidemesh app icon."
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrap hero-facts">
        <div>
          <b>Own the host</b>
          <p>Keep code, credentials, terminals, and development servers on your own machines.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <b>See the session</b>
          <p>Carry more than chat: approvals, files, ports, previews, and host state stay visible.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <b>Stay private</b>
          <p>Pair over Tailscale, a VPN, or a trusted LAN instead of exposing host control casually.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="what">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">What it is</span>
          <h2>Not a cloud IDE. A control plane for your own agent hosts.</h2>
          <p>
            The useful part is not only sending prompts. It is having enough of
            the host available to review work, unblock sessions, and continue
            from a phone or another desktop without moving the code anywhere
            else.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rails">
          <article class="rail">
            <strong>Sessions stay visible.</strong>
            <p>
              Recent work, host routing, approvals, and ordered transcript state
              remain reachable when the machine is not in front of you.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="rail">
            <strong>Host surfaces stay attached.</strong>
            <p>
              Files, terminals, forwarded ports, previews, and usage are part of
              the same story instead of a separate toolchain.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="rail">
            <strong>The network boundary stays explicit.</strong>
            <p>
              Sidemesh is powerful because it sits close to the host. The route
              should stay private for the same reason.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

