              <code>sidemesh up</code>, and use the pairing details it prints.
            </p>
            <div class="command-strip mono" aria-label="Host install commands">
              <span>$ npm install -g sidemesh @openai/codex</span>
              <span>$ sidemesh up</span>
              <span>$ sidemesh service install</span>
            </div>
            <div class="install-actions">
              <a class="button secondary" href="/getting-started/">Read the docs</a>
